Affiliation = {DeCastro-García, N (Corresponding Author), Univ Leon, Res Inst Appl Sci Cybersecur, Campus Vegazana S-N, Leon 24007, Spain.
   DeCastro-García, N (Corresponding Author), Univ Leon, Dept Math, Campus Vegazana S-N, Leon 24007, Spain.
