   Stamenkovic, Zoran, Leibniz Inst Innovat Mikroelekt, IHP, D-15236 Frankfurt, Oder, Germany.
   Barbas, Piotr, Natl Res Inst, Plant Breeding \& Acclimatizat Inst, Dept Potato Agron, Branch Jadwisin, PL-05140 Serock, Poland.
