   Ren, Yuchen, China Univ Min \& Technol, Xuzhou 221116, Peoples R China.
   Xu, Hao, Chinese Acad Forestry, Inst Chem Ind Forest Prod, Jiangsu Prov Biomass \& Mat Lab, Nanjing 210042, Peoples R China.},
