   Chen, Yihao, Chinese Acad Med Sci CAMS, Lab Pathogen Infect Prevent \& Control, State Key Lab Resp Hlth \& Multimorbid, Minist Educ,Natl Inst Pathogen Biol,Peking Union C, Beijing, Peoples R China.
   Gao, Yinyan, Cent South Univ, Xiangya Sch Publ Hlth, Dept Epidemiol \& Biostat, Changsha, Hunan, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1245/s10434-026-19263-3},
