Affiliation = {Tun, KJG (Corresponding Author), Univ Guadalajara, Dept Water \& Energy, Campus Tonala, Tonala 45425, Mexico.
   Bravo, Martin Antonio Hernandez; Tun, Kelly Joel Gurubel, Univ Guadalajara, Dept Water \& Energy, Campus Tonala, Tonala 45425, Mexico.
