   Carpenter, Timothy S.; Aydin, Fikret; Zhang, Xiaohua; Georgouli, Konstantia; Tempkin, Jeremy O. B.; Oppelstrup, Tomas; Glosli, James N.; Dharuman, Gautham; Wong, Sergio; Lightstone, Felice C.; Ingolfsson, Helgi I., Lawrence Livermore Natl Lab, Phys \& Life Sci PLS Directorate, Livermore, CA 94550 USA.
   Neale, Chris; Casamayor, Violeta Burns; Hengartner, Nicolas W.; Lopez, Cesar A.; Nguyen, Kien; Patel, Lara; Reddy, Tyler; Turbyville, Thomas J.; Stephen, Andrew G.; Gnanakaran, Sandrasegaram, Los Alamos Natl Lab, Theoret Biol \& Biophys Grp, Los Alamos, NM USA.
