Affiliation = {Sun, J; Li, X; Su, ZM (Corresponding Author), Changchun Univ Sci \& Technol, Jilin Prov Sci \& Technol Innovat Ctr Opt Mat \& Che, Sch Chem \& Environm Engn, Changchun, Peoples R China.
