   Bello, Usman; Amran, Nurul Aini, Univ Teknol PETRONAS, Chem Engn Dept, Seri Iskandar 32610, Perak, Malaysia.
   Bello, Usman; Amran, Nurul Aini, Univ Teknol PETRONAS, Inst Sustainable Energy \& Resources, HICoE Ctr Biofuel \& Biochem Res CBBR, Seri Iskandar 32610, Perak, Malaysia.
