   Gebhardt-Henrich, Sabine G., Univ Bern, Vet Publ Hlth Inst, Ctr Proper Housing Poultry \& Rabbits ZTHZ, Anim Welf Div, Zollikofen, Switzerland.
   Fischer-Tenhagen, Carola, German Fed Inst Risk Assessment, German Ctr Protect Lab Anim Bf3R, Berlin, Germany.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.psj.2025.106141},
