   Zouhri, Lahcen, UniLaSalle Beauvais, AGHYLE, Inst Polytech, 19 Rue Pierre Waguet, F-60026 Beauvais, France.
   Abdelkarim, Bilel, Pole Univ Minho, Inst Earth Sci, Campus Gualtar, P-4710057 Braga, Portugal.
   Abdelkarim, Bilel, Univ Beira Interior, Fiber Mat \& Environm Technol FibEnTech UBI, R Marques Avila \& Bolama, P-6201001 Covilha, Portugal.
   Zghibi, Adel, Univ Tunis El Manar, Fac Sci Tunis, LR01ES06 Lab Ressources Minerales \& Environm, Tunis 2092, Tunisia.},
DOI = {10.3390/hydrology12120326},
