   Abd Elsalam, Hassan E.; El Azab, Islam H., Taif Univ, Coll Sci, Dept Food Sci \& Nutr, POB 11099, Taif 21944, Saudi Arabia.
   Waheeb, Azal S., Al Ayen Univ, Sci Res Ctr, Inorgan Chem Grp, Thi Qar, Iraq.
   Kyhoiesh, Hussein A. K., Republ Iraq Minist Educ, Gen Directorate Educ Al Muthanna, Samawah, Al Muthanna, Iraq.},
DOI = {10.1039/d5ra06776f},
Author-Email = {hussein.k.sultan@nust.edu.iq},
