   Manna, Manpreet Singh, St Longowal Inst Engn \& Technol, Elect \& Instrumentat Engn, Longowal, Punjab, India.
   Bhattacharya, Shantanu, Indian Inst Technol Kanpur, Dept Mech Engn, Kanpur 208016, India.
