   strategy was more resistant to temperature perturbation, had a longer
   stable operation time, and could reach an average daily methane
   production of 379.85 +/- 5.44 mL/g VS. This study provides guidance and
   regulatory methods for enhancing methane production performance in AD
   systems with TEs.},
