   Alyami, Geamel; Shaman, Hussein, King Abdulaziz City Sci \& Technol, Riyadh, Saudi Arabia.
   Singh, Narinderjit Singh Sawaran, INTI Int Univ, Fac Data Sci \& Informat Technol, Nilai, Malaysia.
   Abdallah, Hanaa A., Princess Nourah Bint Abdulrahman Univ, Coll Comp \& Informat Sci, Dept Informat Technol, POB 84428, Riyadh 11671, Saudi Arabia.
