   Tran, Thanh-Nam, Ton Duc Thang Univ, Fac Informat Technol, Data Sci Lab, 19 Nguyen Huu Tho, Ho Chi Minh 70000, Vietnam.
   Mesicek, Jakub; Pagac, Marek, VSB Tech Univ Ostrava, Fac Mech Engn, Dept Machining Assembly \& Engn Metrol, Ostrava 70833, Czech Republic.},
DOI = {10.17973/MMSJ.2025\_10\_2025095},
