   Rajendran, Anitha Kumari; Govindan, Suresh, N Rama Varier Ayurveda Fdn, Madurai, Tamil Nadu, India.
   Rajendran, Anitha Kumari; Govindan, Suresh, AVN Ayurveda Formulat Pvt Ltd, Madurai, Tamil Nadu, India.},
DOI = {10.1111/ppl.70536},
