   Zhou, Yuxin; Mo, Hongzhi, Shanghai Univ, Shanghai Acad Fine Arts, Dept Architecture, Shanghai 200444, Peoples R China.
   Zhou, Yuxin; Mo, Hongzhi, Shanghai Univ, Shanghai Acad Fine Arts, Dept Architecture, Lab Built Environm, Shanghai 200444, Peoples R China.
   Wang, Kun, Henan Agr Univ, Coll Landscape Architecture \& Art, Zhengzhou 450002, Peoples R China.
   Zhang, Taoyuan, Hefei Univ Technol, Coll Architecture \& Art, Hefei 230009, Peoples R China.
   Yin, Shi, South China Univ Technol, Sch Architecture, Guangzhou 510641, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.enbuild.2025.116465},
EarlyAccessDate = {SEP 2025},
