   Zhao, Yuhong, North Univ China, Sch Mat Sci \& Engn, Taiyuan 030051, Peoples R China.
   Fu, Huadong; Xie, Jianxin, Liaoning Acad Mat, Inst Mat Intelligent Technol, Shenyang 110004, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.ijplas.2025.104461},
EarlyAccessDate = {SEP 2025},
