Abstract = {This work presents a comprehensive nonlinear dynamic analysis of
   moderately thick car hood doors reinforced with graphene oxide-carbon
   nanotube (GO-CNT) as the hybrid nanocomposites. The structural
   configuration is modeled as a doubly car hood door, and geometric
   nonlinearities are captured using the sinusoidal shear deformation
