   Gautam, Shivam K., Chungnam Natl Univ, Dept Elect Engn, Korea Sensor Lab, Daejeon, South Korea.
   Kuppireddy, Suresh; Lee, Hi-Deok, Technol Innovat Inst, Renewable \& Sustainable Energy Res Ctr, POB 9639, Abu Dhabi, U Arab Emirates.
