   Bao, Li, Qiqihar Univ, Sch Mech \& Elect Engn, Qiqihar 161000, Peoples R China.
   Lu, Rihuan, Yanshan Univ, Natl Engn Res Ctr Equipment \& Technol Cold Rolled, Qinhuangdao 066004, Peoples R China.},
