   Fujii, M (Corresponding Author), Nara Inst Sci \& Technol, Data Sci Ctr, Ikoma, Nara 6300192, Japan.
   Nishimura, Takuma; Kumabe, Yoshitaka; Tachikawa, Takashi, Kobe Univ, Grad Sch Sci, Dept Chem, Kobe 6578501, Japan.
